"title": "5433: occupations",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5433",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Professions, trades and means of employment. A great variety of occupations, both secular and religious, are mentioned in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Builders</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:1\">PSA 127:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22\">PSA 118:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:42\">MAT 21:42</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:10\">MRK 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:17\">LUK 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:11\">ACT 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:10-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:10–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:3\">HEB 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:7\">1PE 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Embroiderers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:23\">EXO 38:23</a></p>\n<h2>Weavers and spinners</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:22\">EXO 39:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:19\">PRO 31:19</a></p>\n<h2>Stonemasons</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:12\">2KI 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:5-2Kgs22:6\">2KI 22:5–22:6</a></p>\n<h2>Carpenters and woodworkers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:5-2Kgs22:6\">2KI 22:5–22:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:55\">MAT 13:55</a></p>\n<h2>Musicians</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:19-1Chr15:22\">1CH 15:19–15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:42\">1CH 16:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:19\">HAB 3:19</a></p>\n<h2>Tanners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:43\">ACT 9:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:6\">ACT 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:32\">ACT 10:32</a></p>\n<h2>Linen workers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:21\">1CH 4:21</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Washermen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:3\">ISA 7:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:17\">2KI 18:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:2\">ISA 36:2</a></p>\n<h2>Blacksmiths</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:12\">ISA 44:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:19-1Sam13:21\">1SA 13:19–13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:16\">ISA 54:16</a></p>\n<h2>Merchants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:31-Neh3:32\">NEH 3:31–3:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:14-1Kgs10:15\">1KI 10:14–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:28-1Kgs10:29\">1KI 10:28–10:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:16-2Chr1:17\">2CH 1:16–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:19-Neh13:21\">NEH 13:19–13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:7\">HOS 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:45-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:45–13:46</a></p>\n<h2>Tentmakers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:1-Acts18:3\">ACT 18:1–18:3</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Soldiers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:1\">2KI 5:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:5-Matt8:13\">MAT 8:5–8:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:1-Luke7:10\">LUK 7:1–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:14\">LUK 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:1-Acts10:8\">ACT 10:1–10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:3-2Tim2:4\">2TI 2:3–2:4</a></p>\n<h2>Priests</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen46:20\">GEN 46:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:18\">GEN 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:1\">EXO 18:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:3\">EXO 28:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:13\">EXO 40:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:12-Judg17:13\">JDG 17:12–17:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:27-1Sam2:29\">1SA 2:27–2:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:2-1Kgs4:5\">1KI 4:2–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:7\">MAL 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:4\">MAT 8:4</a></p>\n<h2>Levites and temple servants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:50-Num1:51\">NUM 1:50–1:51</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:16\">1CH 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:22\">1CH 15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:4\">1CH 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:70\">EZR 2:70</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:44-Neh12:47\">NEH 12:44–12:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:32\">LUK 10:32</a></p>\n<h2>Watchmen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:1\">PSA 127:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:24-2Sam18:27\">2SA 18:24–18:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:1-Song3:4\">SNG 3:1–3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:7\">SNG 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:11-Isa21:12\">ISA 21:11–21:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:10\">ISA 56:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:2-Ezek33:6\">EZK 33:2–33:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1-John10:3\">JHN 10:1–10:3</a></p>\n<h2>Shepherds</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:3\">GEN 47:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:1-Gen29:10\">GEN 29:1–29:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen46:31-Gen46:34\">GEN 46:31–46:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:16-Exod2:17\">EXO 2:16–2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:20\">1SA 17:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:7\">1SA 21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:1\">AMO 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:8-Luke2:18\">LUK 2:8–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:2-John10:4\">JHN 10:2–10:4</a></p>\n<h2>Farmers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:4-Zech13:5\">ZEC 13:4–13:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:24-Isa28:25\">ISA 28:24–28:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:5\">JER 31:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:11\">JOL 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:3-Matt13:9\">MAT 13:3–13:9</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:3-Mark4:8\">MRK 4:3–4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:5-Luke8:8\">LUK 8:5–8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:33\">MAT 21:33</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:1\">MRK 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:9\">LUK 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:6\">2TI 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7\">JAS 5:7</a></p>\n<h2>Fishermen</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:48\">MAT 13:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:8\">ISA 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:16\">JER 16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:10\">EZK 47:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:18-Matt4:19\">MAT 4:18–4:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:16-Mark1:17\">MRK 1:16–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:2\">LUK 5:2</a></p>\n<h2>Doctors</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:25-Mark5:26\">MRK 5:25–5:26</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:43\">LUK 8:43</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:12\">MAT 9:12</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:17\">MRK 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:31\">LUK 5:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:14\">COL 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Lawyers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:1\">ACT 24:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:13\">TIT 3:13</a></p>",
